[CDC is encouraging local and state health departments to test for
noroviruses when investigating outbreaks of suspected viral acute
gastroenteritis. For assistance in testing for noroviruses and for strain
characterization, local and state health departments should contact the
CDC's Viral Gastroenteritis Section: email <CaliciNet@cdc.gov>. - Mod.MPP]
